import React from "react"; import { FiCamera, FiCalendar } from "react-icons/fi"; const CameraMetadata = ({ photo }) => { return (

Camera: {photo.camera}

Lens: {photo.lens}

Aperture: {photo.settings.aperture}
Shutter: {photo.settings.shutter}
ISO: {photo.settings.iso}
Focal Length: {photo.settings.focalLength}

Date: {new Date(photo.date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}

); }; export default CameraMetadata;
